text: Ileana Gyarfaş (born 8 January 1932) is a Romanian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cluj-Napoca
